{"tid":1014110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我留左電話同名比個傳道士","createTime":"2019-02-09T02:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T04:18:59.000Z","uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b06c99405224bd47883d1528fd1059b11fd40d","tid":1014110,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"基督教嫁<br />\n佢拍門上黎<br />\n我又衰心軟聽佢傳道<br />\n聽左好奈好奈，覺得好煩<br />\n我仲記得當時食野中唔想理佢，就是但比左電話<br />\n估唔到佢咁煩<br />\n你話一兩次就算啦<br />\n佢仲要間中拍門上黎傳教<br />\n次次我都係食野中，阻住曬<br />\n之後我電話block左佢<br />\n佢都仲上黎搵我傳教<br />\n走啦<br />\n我冇興趣聽你講野啊"},{"pid":"963b436742e3b2405d494b22d6f13ecab092cc5d","tid":1014110,"uid":30578,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:12:20.000Z","msg":"你大撚獲"},{"pid":"fdcf4e727fc9d2cdff7761dd9349f4c59041668e","tid":1014110,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"963b436742e3b2405d494b22d6f13ecab092cc5d","tid":1014110,"uid":30578,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:12:20.000Z","msg":"你大撚獲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n好似已經係1年幾前開始了<br />\n開頭仲成日whatapp 我<br />\nsend教會啲活動比我睇<br />\n叫我參加下<br />\n又send一大段聖經同成日上黎拍門搵我<br />\n後尾我block左佢都算好好多了<br />\n但今日又上黎拍門搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c129f9268b92a9a87221f0f6be61da7ced5f564","tid":1014110,"uid":161174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"我已經同佢講左我係天主教<br />\n佢仲好似搵到同好咁，覺得我對聖經好有興趣<br />\n係咁捉住我講<br />\n我父母已經幫我開門推左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05ac047e3a373cf3ea0c920c4b6635087320dfd","tid":1014110,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"點解你比電話佢會知你住邊"},{"pid":"8cb5af276a04c6f7e71d6ffa607cb33157f23040","tid":1014110,"uid":36993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"守望台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.